Life doesn't have so many "what ifs".

11
00:01:19,360 --> 00:01:20,720
(What do I do?)

12
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:22,480
(I need to find a way out of here.)

13
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:29,200
(Isn't this the inn)

14
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,600
