20
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,840
I can't wait anymore.

21
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:54,600
Mom.

22
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:55,760
Pull over.

23
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:01,280
Stay with Zhiyi.

24
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,120
Okay.

25
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:21,560
What's wrong, Miss Qin?

26
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,400
It hurts too much.

27
00:02:22,600 --> 00:02:24,160
Please get me some medicine.

28
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:26,240
Well...

29
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,720
If it gets worse,

30
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:28,300
I'll tell Mom

31
00:02:28,300 --> 00:02:29,640
- it's your fault.
- Go quickly.

32
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,320
Okay.

33
00:02:36,040 --> 00:02:36,880
Miss Qin!

34
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:38,960
Miss Qin, stop running!

35
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:41,260
It's dangerous!

36
00:02:41,260 --> 00:02:42,680
How will I explain to President Qin?

37
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:45,550
Miss Qin,

38
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,400
why are you running?

39
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,440
What's wrong with you?

40
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:56,080
(This time,)

41
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:58,080
(no matter the cost,)

42
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,840
(I need to live for myself.)

43
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:14,640
Sir.

44
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,080
Can I borrow your phone?

45
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,880
Please, sir.

46
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:21,080
Just for a moment.

47
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:24,560
Thank you.

48
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:34,680
Zhou Nanfeng,

49
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,640
it's me.

50
00:03:36,050 --> 00:03:36,920
I'm hurt.

51
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:39,750
I'm at Houhai Inn.

52
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:47,920
What's the use of you?

53
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,040
Couldn't even watch her properly.

54
00:03:53,480 --> 00:03:54,320
Ms. Qin,

55
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:55,200
Zhiyi's phone

56
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:56,320
