61
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,920
Keep monitoring their phones

62
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:08,920
and their bank cards.

63
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:10,320
We must find them.

64
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:11,160
- Yes.
- Yes.

65
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,200
Let me see.

66
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,320
Where are you hurt?

67
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,160
You lied to me.

68
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:27,800
Wait a moment.

69
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:29,360
I know everything now.

70
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,120
Xingyue told me all of it.

71
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,080
Stop pushing me away.

72
00:04:37,670 --> 00:04:39,650
I'm not Zhou Nanfeng
from your space-time.

73
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:42,080
But I'm Qin Zhiyi in this space-time.

74
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:44,080
In this space-time,

75
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:46,360
do we have to miss each other again?

76
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:47,640
I know,

77
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:49,760
I'm in your heart.

78
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,840
Otherwise, why rush over

79
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,740
